<mj-section>
  <mj-column>
    <mj-text
      font-size="24px"
      font-weight="bold"
      color="#4a4a4a"
      align="center"
      padding-bottom="20px"
    >
      Your Trial is Ending Soon ⏰
    </mj-text>

    <mj-text> Hey {{name}}! 👋 </mj-text>

    <mj-text>
      Just a heads up - your free trial of Minova Pro is wrapping up on
      <strong>{{trialEndDate}}</strong>.
    </mj-text>

    <mj-text>
      When your trial ends, we'll automatically charge {{currency}} {{firstBillingAmount}} to keep
      all your premium features running smoothly.
    </mj-text>

    <mj-text>
      <strong>All the good stuff you'll keep enjoying with Minova Pro: 🌟</strong>
    </mj-text>

    <mj-text padding-left="25px">
      • Unlimited resume matching<br />
      • Advanced AI-powered job recommendations<br />
      • Custom resume templates<br />
      • Priority support<br />
      • And much more!
    </mj-text>

    <mj-button
      background-color="#F7B801"
      color="white"
      border-radius="4px"
      font-weight="bold"
      href="{{manageBillingUrl}}"
    >
      Manage Billing 💳
    </mj-button>

    <mj-text>
      Not ready to commit? No problem! You can cancel anytime before {{trialEndDate}} through your
      billing settings.
    </mj-text>

    <mj-text>
      Thanks for giving Minova Pro a spin! Hope it's been a game-changer for your job search and
      career journey.
    </mj-text>
  </mj-column>
</mj-section>
